  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>印记中文团队</span> <span>2025-10-21 12:55</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">内蒙古</span></p>\n  <p>本期看点：Andreas Rossberg 深入解析 WebAssembly 3.0 的新功能，AsyncTalk 探讨AI时代编程的最佳实践，浪说播客分享前端工程师移居英国的职业选择思考，讨论开源安全问题和 npm 蠕虫攻击</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=81039657&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FINNfEriciaG5e0oH5nEpZlIfazPBxqXwdqFcpad8oSIdYFpQfulTlEWRKHk72FaHLicoGITsvib2QgrJpgxUTCrQDg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100060539\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5518518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3d329c8a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5e0oH5nEpZlIfazPBxqXwdqMOicvt6BDericzSWWBtYkQ4icQdUBXahU0RHDibf6ibS4ObwPMgtHTJnKbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"display: block;font-size: 0.9em;overflow: auto;overflow-scrolling: touch;border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 1.2em;padding-right: 1em;padding-left: 1em;border-left-width: 4px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">本期看点：Andreas Rossberg 深入解析 WebAssembly 3.0 的新功能，AsyncTalk 探讨AI时代编程的最佳实践，浪说播客分享前端工程师移居英国的职业选择思考，Whiskey Web 讨论开源安全问题和 npm 蠕虫攻击，CSS Podcast 探索 2025 年状态查询和自定义函数。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"display: block;font-size: 0.9em;overflow: auto;overflow-scrolling: touch;border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 1.2em;padding-right: 1em;padding-left: 1em;border-left-width: 4px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：Otto 辛宝、TimLi</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;color: black;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">PodRocket：深度解析 WebAssembly 3.0 新功能</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Andreas Rossberg 深入解析 WebAssembly 3.0 的新功能，包括垃圾回收、异常处理、尾调用和 64 位寻址的多内存支持。讨论了确定性配置文件、WebAssembly 基于能力的安全模型，以及在沙盒和模块设计方面的进步。Andreas 将这些特性与 JavaScript 引擎和 Google Sheets 等实际应用场景联系起来，展望了线程、堆栈切换和异步编程模型的实验性工作。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 12px;padding: 16px 20px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.476px;text-align: left;display: flex;align-items: center;background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);box-shadow: rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;border-radius: 6px;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-size: 12px;overflow: hidden;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"http://podrocket.logrocket.com/wasm3-andreas-rossberg\" target=\"_blank\">http://podrocket.logrocket.com/wasm3-andreas-rossberg</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100060532\" data-ratio=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"164\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=af7a47ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5e0oH5nEpZlIfazPBxqXwdqGISohseBW9dl1Aiaa1zySaPbgibKFRMAUcRDl20AtHuNk81Xhs6tORNw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;color: black;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">浪说播客：蜗牛老湿的英伦码农生活</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 本期节目讲述了一位前端工程师\"大圣\"在北京打拼17年后移居英国的真实经历。面对国内互联网行业的\"内卷\"与35岁危机焦虑，他在疫情后为家庭和未来教育考虑，选择踏上英国寻找新的可能性。节目深入探讨了程序员在海外工作的现实挑战与机遇，从薪资水平到工作文化差异，从教育环境到生活成本，为考虑海外发展的开发者提供了宝贵的参考经验，引发了对\"更高天花板还是更稳底线\"这一职业选择核心问题的深度思考。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 12px;padding: 16px 20px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.476px;text-align: left;display: flex;align-items: center;background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);box-shadow: rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;border-radius: 6px;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-size: 12px;overflow: hidden;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/68eede408bc215dc6e9ce08a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/68eede408bc215dc6e9ce08a</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100060530\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"164\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2737d1f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5e0oH5nEpZlIfazPBxqXwdqGlQs9PEJcfV5FdUFg2PQWlwiawTK4oIcLJSuwsyHb612kHF7pSgNXuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;color: black;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">AsyncTalk：EP48 AI 来了，代码该这么写才能从从容容游刃有余</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 本期节目深入探讨了如何在AI时代保持编程优势的核心问题。节目提出了几个关键观点：程序员的可扩展逻辑思维仍然难以替代，后端开发应该选择Node.js，代码可读性应该优先于一切其他要求。讨论了AI时代的技术栈选择（Next.js、Tailwind CSS + shadcn）、开发原则（可访问性优先、XML优于JSON、支持标准IO），以及核心编程哲学——可读性高于性能、效率和短期收益。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 12px;padding: 16px 20px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.476px;text-align: left;display: flex;align-items: center;background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);box-shadow: rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;border-radius: 6px;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-size: 12px;overflow: hidden;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/68f66104c4a8670d2edc9824\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/68f66104c4a8670d2edc9824</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100060531\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"164\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c265281&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5e0oH5nEpZlIfazPBxqXwdq1STnic0FFt7MnADLRbo7ghxEgicjsJlRzPSVYW3FV6GUyg8NRHBjyUzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;color: black;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: black;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Whiskey Web and Whatnot：npm 蠕虫与 RubyGems 政变：开源信任问题</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Robbie、Chuck 和 Adam 讨论了开源领域最近的安全恐慌，包括 npm 蠕虫攻击和 RubyGems 的信任问题。他们深入分析了依赖管理卫生、开发者签证混乱，以及科技薪资膨胀是否正在得到纠正。还探讨了 Tailwind 作为\"状态管理库\"的争议，以及 AI 工具的专业化趋势，为开发者提供了开源安全的重要洞察。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 12px;padding: 16px 20px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.476px;text-align: left;display: flex;align-items: center;background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);box-shadow: rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;border-radius: 6px;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-size: 12px;overflow: hidden;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;